'''Tion Industries''' was a company which included such subsidiaries as [[Tion Mil/Sci Industries/Legends|Tion Mil/Sci Industries]] and the [[Civil Aeronautics Division]]. It manufactured the [[Hyperfoil 1000-XTC]] and the [[Guardian-class patrol ship|''Guardian''-class patrol ship]].

